{"parse":{"title":"Shake Hands with the Devil (book)","pageid":1040940,"revid":816400605,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">For other uses, see <a href=\"/wiki/Shake_Hands_with_the_Devil_(disambiguation)\" class=\"mw-redirect mw-disambig\" title=\"Shake Hands with the Devil (disambiguation)\">Shake Hands with the Devil (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption style=\"font-style:italic;padding-bottom:0.2em;\">Shake Hands with the Devil <span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Shake+Hands+with+the+Devil&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BRom%C3%A9o+Dallaire%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=September+2003&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BRandom+House+of+Canada%23Random+House+Canada%7CRandom+House+Canada%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/50022773\"></span></caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;display:none\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Rom%C3%A9o_Dallaire\" title=\"Rom\u00e9o Dallaire\">Rom\u00e9o Dallaire</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\nCanada</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Random_House_of_Canada#Random_House_Canada\" title=\"Random House of Canada\">Random House Canada</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Publication date</div></th><td>\nSeptember 2003</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a></th><td>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-679-31171-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-679-31171-3\">978-0-679-31171-3</a> (0-679-31171-8) /\n</p>\n978-0-679-31172-0 (0-679-31172-6)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/OCLC#Identifiers_and_linked_data\" title=\"OCLC\"><abbr title=\"Online Computer Library Center number\">OCLC</abbr></a></th><td>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/50022773\">50022773</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/Library_of_Congress_Classification\" title=\"Library of Congress Classification\"><abbr title=\"Library of Congress Classification\">LC&#160;Class</abbr></a></th><td>\nDT450.435 .D35 2003</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Shake Hands with the Devil: The Failure of Humanity in Rwanda</b></i> is a book by <a href=\"/wiki/Lieutenant-General\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lieutenant-General\">Lieutenant-General</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Rom%C3%A9o_Dallaire\" title=\"Rom\u00e9o Dallaire\">Rom\u00e9o Dallaire</a> of the <a href=\"/wiki/Canadian_Forces\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Canadian Forces\">Canadian Forces</a>, with help from Major Brent Beardsley. It was first published by <a href=\"/wiki/Random_House_of_Canada#Random_House_Canada\" title=\"Random House of Canada\">Random House Canada</a> in September 2003.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/52/Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg/220px-Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"293\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/52/Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg/330px-Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/52/Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg/440px-Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1200\" data-file-height=\"1600\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Romeo_Dallaire_signing.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Romeo Dallaire signing <i>Shake Hands with the Devil</i></div></div></div>\n<p>The book chronicles Dallaire's tour as Force Commander of the <a href=\"/wiki/United_Nations_Assistance_Mission_for_Rwanda\" title=\"United Nations Assistance Mission for Rwanda\">United Nations Assistance Mission for Rwanda</a> (UNAMIR) in 1993-1994, during which he witnessed the 1994 <a href=\"/wiki/Rwandan_Genocide\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rwandan Genocide\">Rwandan Genocide</a>.\n</p><p>The book won the 2003 <a href=\"/wiki/Shaughnessy_Cohen_Award_for_Political_Writing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shaughnessy Cohen Award for Political Writing\">Shaughnessy Cohen Award for Political Writing</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/2004_Governor_General%27s_Awards\" title=\"2004 Governor General&#39;s Awards\">2004 Governor General's Award</a> for nonfiction.\n</p><p>The edition published in French is entitled <i>J'ai serr\u00e9 la main du diable: La faillite de l'humanit\u00e9 au Rwanda</i>.\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/wiki/Documentary_film\" title=\"Documentary film\">documentary film</a> <i><a href=\"/wiki/Shake_Hands_with_the_Devil:_The_Journey_of_Rom%C3%A9o_Dallaire\" title=\"Shake Hands with the Devil: The Journey of Rom\u00e9o Dallaire\">Shake Hands with the Devil: The Journey of Rom\u00e9o Dallaire</a></i> (2004) and a <a href=\"/wiki/Shake_Hands_with_the_Devil_(2007_film)\" title=\"Shake Hands with the Devil (2007 film)\">2007 dramatic feature film</a> are inspired by and in part based on the book. Dallaire was consulted in the making of both films.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Shake_Hands_with_the_Devil_(book)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20041208223408/http://www.randomhouse.ca/readmag/volume4issue2/excerpts/aboutshakehandswiththedevil.htm\">\"About <i>Shake Hands With the Devil: The Failure of Humanity in Rwanda.</i>\"</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-top: 5px solid #FFF179;\">Awards\n</th></tr>\n\n<tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Peacemakers:_The_Paris_Peace_Conference_of_1919_and_Its_Attempt_to_End_War\" title=\"Peacemakers: The Paris Peace Conference of 1919 and Its Attempt to End War\">Paris 1919: Six Months That Changed the World</a></i></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/wiki/Governor_General%27s_Award_for_English_language_non-fiction\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Governor General&#39;s Award for English language non-fiction\">Governor General's Award for English language non-fiction recipient</a></b><br /><a href=\"/wiki/2004_in_literature\" title=\"2004 in literature\">2004</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<br /><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"><i>The Golden Spruce: A True Story of Myth, Madness and Greed</i></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Africa.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Africa.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Africa.svg/32px-Africa.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Africa.svg/48px-Africa.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b4/Africa.svg/64px-Africa.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"633\" data-file-height=\"792\" /></a><img alt=\"Hourglass drawing.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c2/Hourglass_drawing.svg/22px-Hourglass_drawing.svg.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"29\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c2/Hourglass_drawing.svg/33p